        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You died and came back, but your return to life was no miracle, and you didn't glimpse paradise. You were trapped for eons in cold darkness cast in perfect silence. You became a speck crushed at the center of a black hole. You saw the Afterlight, and now it's always waiting for you behind your eyelids.</p>\n<p>Choose two attribute boosts. One must be to <strong>Constitution</strong> or <strong>Wisdom</strong>, and one is a free attribute boost.</p>\n<p>You gain the Diehard feat and the @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.feats.Item.Additional Lore] feat for Eox Lore or Undead Lore.</p>"
